---
// Reviews component
---

<section
  id="reviews"
  class="py-24 bg-brand-cream border-t border-brand-dark/10"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2
        class="text-brand-bordeaux text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-bold mb-4"
      >
        Livre d'or
      </h2>
      <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-brand-dark">
        Ce que disent nos convives
      </h3>
      <div class="flex justify-center mt-6 space-x-1 text-brand-gold">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 20 20"
          ><path
            d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 20 20"
          ><path
            d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 20 20"
          ><path
            d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 20 20"
          ><path
            d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 20 20"
          ><path
            d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      {/* Review 1 */}
      <div
        class="bg-white p-8 rounded-sm shadow-md border border-brand-dark/5 flex flex-col items-center text-center"
      >
        <p class="text-brand-dark/80 italic font-light mb-6 grow">
          "Une véritable institution. Retrouver l'œuf mayo de mon enfance et
          cette ambiance si particulière du vieux Paris... C'est toujours un
          bonheur d'y venir dîner."
        </p>
        <div>
          <span class="block font-serif text-lg text-brand-dark"
            >Jean-Pierre M.</span
          >
          <span class="text-xs text-brand-dark/50 uppercase tracking-widest"
            >Habitué</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Review 2 */}
      <div
        class="bg-brand-dark-wood p-8 rounded-sm shadow-xl transform md:-translate-y-4 border border-brand-gold/20 flex flex-col items-center text-center relative"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute -top-4 w-8 h-8 bg-brand-bordeaux rotate-45 flex items-center justify-center"
        >
          <span class="text-brand-gold -rotate-45 font-serif text-xl">"</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-brand-cream/90 italic font-light mb-6 grow mt-4">
          "Le fumoir à cigares est exceptionnel. Certainement l'un des secrets
          les mieux gardés de la capitale. La sélection de vieux rhums est à
          tomber."
        </p>
        <div>
          <span class="block font-serif text-lg text-brand-gold"
            >Alexandre L.</span
          >
          <span class="text-xs text-brand-cream/50 uppercase tracking-widest"
            >Guide Michelin</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Review 3 */}
      <div
        class="bg-white p-8 rounded-sm shadow-md border border-brand-dark/5 flex flex-col items-center text-center"
      >
        <p class="text-brand-dark/80 italic font-light mb-6 grow">
          "Un service impeccable de bout en bout. Le ballet des serveurs aux
          grands tabliers blancs ajoute à la magie du lieu. La sole meunière
          était divine."
        </p>
        <div>
          <span class="block font-serif text-lg text-brand-dark">Claire T.</span
          >
          <span class="text-xs text-brand-dark/50 uppercase tracking-widest"
            >Sur Google</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
